sec.p:
Literature inclusion criteria:
population: patients who underwent total gastrectomy with clear pathology of GC;
interventions: patients who received RTG;
control: patients who received LTG;
outcomes: metrics included efficacy aspects;
study design: RCT, retrospective studies, and prospective studies.

Literature exclusion criteria:
reviews, conference proceedings, or commentaries;
duplicate literature (retaining the variant with the most comprehensive information);
no relevant outcome metrics;
no use of total gastrectomy.
